spatially enable srdb:

psql srdb -f /usr/share/postgresql-8.2-postgis/lwpostgis.sql
psql srdb -f /usr/share/postgresql-8.2-postgis/spatial_ref_sys.sql


LME shapefile obtained from http://www.lme.noaa.gov

unzip the archive lmes_64.zip

produce SQL from shapefile:
shp2pgsql LMEs_64 -s 4326 lmes > lmes.sql

load into srdb:
psql srdb -f lmes.sql
